&lt;p&gt;One other FYI, this jira is assigned to be fixed in 3.4.0 (current trunk, ie the next full trunk release). Typically you&apos;d want to create the patch against svn trunk. Also, the patch queue on hudson (qa bot) will only test patches against trunk. Not a big deal (your patch may apply against trunk even if created from 3.3.1) but I just wanted to give you that headsup.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks again. Regards.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
